sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant R as Router
    participant Cu as Curator
    participant Re as Researcher
    participant B as Builder
    participant Ctx as Context
    participant API as tRPC API

    U->>R: "Create a project for mobile app redesign and show me related tasks"
    R->>R: Analyze intent
    Note over R: Detect: Create + Organize + Display

    R->>Ctx: Update context with request
    R->>Cu: Create project object
    Cu->>API: object.create({type: 'project', ...})
    API-->>Cu: Created project
    Cu->>Ctx: Store project ID
    Cu-->>U: "Created 'Mobile App Redesign' project"

    R->>Re: Find related tasks
    Re->>API: search.semantic("mobile app tasks")
    API-->>Re: Related tasks
    Re->>Ctx: Store found tasks
    Re-->>U: "Found 5 related tasks"

    R->>B: Generate project view
    B->>Ctx: Get project + tasks
    B->>B: Generate UI component
    B-->>U: Stream Kanban component

    U-->>U: View rendered Kanban board
